{"word":"δορυφορέω","slug":"δορυφορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δορυφορέω</b></el> <el>(δορῠφορέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δορυφόρος'><el>δορυφόρος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to attend as a bodyguard</i>, <el>τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: generally, <i>to keep guard over</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be guarded</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>δ. τινι</el> <i>to serve as guard</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}